{"cnd4:0.1":"Culaniddesa ","cnd4:0.2":"Parayanavaggagatha ","cnd4:0.3":"4. Parayananugitigatha ","cnd4:1.1":"“Parayanamanugayissam, ","cnd4:1.2":"(iccayasma pingiyo) ","cnd4:1.3":"Yathaddakkhi tathakkhasi; ","cnd4:1.4":"Vimalo bhurimedhaso, ","cnd4:1.5":"Nikkamo nibbano nago; ","cnd4:1.6":"Kissa hetu musa bhane. ","cnd4:2.1":"Pahinamalamohassa, ","cnd4:2.2":"manamakkhappahayino; ","cnd4:2.3":"Handaham kittayissami, ","cnd4:2.4":"giram vannupasanhitam. ","cnd4:3.1":"Tamonudo buddho samantacakkhu, ","cnd4:3.2":"Lokantagu sabbabhavativatto; ","cnd4:3.3":"Anasavo sabbadukkhappahino, ","cnd4:3.4":"Saccavhayo brahme upasito me. ","cnd4:4.1":"Dijo yatha kubbanakam pahaya, ","cnd4:4.2":"Bahupphalam kananamavaseyya; ","cnd4:4.3":"Evampaham appadasse pahaya, ","cnd4:4.4":"Mahodadhim hamsoriva ajjhapatto. ","cnd4:5.1":"Yeme pubbe viyakamsu, ","cnd4:5.2":"Huram gotamasasana; ","cnd4:5.3":"Iccasi iti bhavissati, ","cnd4:5.4":"Sabbam tam itihitiham; ","cnd4:5.5":"Sabbam tam takkavaddhanam. ","cnd4:6.1":"Eko tamonudasino, ","cnd4:6.2":"jutima so pabhankaro; ","cnd4:6.3":"Gotamo bhuripannano, ","cnd4:6.4":"gotamo bhurimedhaso. ","cnd4:7.1":"Yo me dhammamadesesi, ","cnd4:7.2":"Sanditthikamakalikam; ","cnd4:7.3":"Tanhakkhayamanitikam, ","cnd4:7.4":"Yassa natthi upama kvaci”. ","cnd4:8.1":"“Kim nu tamha vippavasasi, ","cnd4:8.2":"muhuttamapi pingiya; ","cnd4:8.3":"Gotama bhuripannana, ","cnd4:8.4":"gotama bhurimedhasa. ","cnd4:9.1":"Yo te dhammamadesesi, ","cnd4:9.2":"Sanditthikamakalikam; ","cnd4:9.3":"Tanhakkhayamanitikam, ","cnd4:9.4":"Yassa natthi upama kvaci”. ","cnd4:10.1":"“Naham tamha vippavasami, ","cnd4:10.2":"Muhuttamapi brahmana; ","cnd4:10.3":"Gotama bhuripannana, ","cnd4:10.4":"Gotama bhurimedhasa. ","cnd4:11.1":"Yo me dhammamadesesi, ","cnd4:11.2":"Sanditthikamakalikam; ","cnd4:11.3":"Tanhakkhayamanitikam, ","cnd4:11.4":"Yassa natthi upama kvaci. ","cnd4:12.1":"Passami nam manasa cakkhunava, ","cnd4:12.2":"Rattindivam brahmana appamatto; ","cnd4:12.3":"Namassamano vivasemi rattim, ","cnd4:12.4":"Teneva mannami avippavasam. ","cnd4:13.1":"Saddha ca piti ca mano sati ca, ","cnd4:13.2":"Napentime gotamasasanamha; ","cnd4:13.3":"Yam yam disam vajati bhuripanno, ","cnd4:13.4":"Sa tena teneva natohamasmi. ","cnd4:14.1":"Jinnassa me dubbalathamakassa, ","cnd4:14.2":"Teneva kayo na paleti tattha; ","cnd4:14.3":"Sankappayantaya vajami niccam, ","cnd4:14.4":"Mano hi me brahmana tena yutto. ","cnd4:15.1":"Panke sayano pariphandamano, ","cnd4:15.2":"Dipa dipam upallavim; ","cnd4:15.3":"Athaddasasim sambuddham, ","cnd4:15.4":"Oghatinnamanasavam”. ","cnd4:16.1":"“Yatha ahu vakkali muttasaddho, ","cnd4:16.2":"Bhadravudho alavigotamo ca; ","cnd4:16.3":"Evameva tvampi pamuncassu saddham, ","cnd4:16.4":"Gamissasi tvam pingiya maccudheyyassa param”. ","cnd4:17.1":"“Esa bhiyyo pasidami, ","cnd4:17.2":"Sutvana munino vaco; ","cnd4:17.3":"Vivattacchado sambuddho, ","cnd4:17.4":"Akhilo patibhanava. ","cnd4:18.1":"Adhideve abhinnaya, ","cnd4:18.2":"Sabbam vedi paroparam; ","cnd4:18.3":"Panhanantakaro sattha, ","cnd4:18.4":"Kankhinam patijanatam. ","cnd4:19.1":"Asamhiram asankuppam, ","cnd4:19.2":"Yassa natthi upama kvaci; ","cnd4:19.3":"Addha gamissami na mettha kankha, ","cnd4:19.4":"Evam mam dharehi adhimuttacittan”ti. ","cnd4:19.5":"Parayananugitigatha nitthita. "}